ence a stunning orchestral score! Hollow Knight\u2019s award-winning composer, Christopher Larkin, brings melancholy melodies, symphonic strings and heart-thumping, soul strumming boss themes to the adventure.","search_queries":["Hollow Knight Silksong"]}},"platforms":["PC"]}','2025-11-04 17:55:57','2025-11-04 19:43:08','2cb4b4bf187f5183efc4d9c712f557828f24bb257745b08c9cc806929c19bf50','An Unofficial free fan demake of the e3 demo of Team Cherry''s Hollow Knight: Silk Song. A new way to experience another masterpiece! Unofficially remade on the GameBoy.','pc',0.55,0,0.915,'{"thegamesdb":"127457"}') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO products (id, name, platform, slug, category, release_date, metadata, created_at, updated_at, uid, synopsis, primary_platform_family, popularity_score, rating, freshness_score, external_ids) VALUES (2299,'Horizon Zapretnyj Zapad','PlayStation 5','horizon-forbidden-west','Game','2022-02-18 00:00:00','{"sources":{"thegamesdb":{"external_id":110527,"category":"Game","platform":"PlayStation 5","players":"1","last_synced_at":"2025-11-04T17:54:40+00:00","search_queries":["Horizon Forbidden West"]}},"platforms":["PlayStation 5"]}','2025-11-04 17:55:57','2025-11-04 19:43:08','03cc7aca481dac638071ba02e0346df1e7da383538276485e5f4d39e7c32b007','Horizon Forbidden West is an action role-playing video game developed by Guerrilla Games and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment for the PlayStation 5. A sequel to 2017''s Horizon Zero Dawn, it is a single-player open world game set in a post-apocalyptic version of the western United States. The player must travel and complete missions using survival skills, melee attacks, and long-distance weapons in a world overrun by a deadly plague, hostile machine creatures, and other survivors.

